      • setBackdrop

        public final void setBackdrop(Boolean backdrop)
        Whether the dialog should have a backdrop or not. Also determines whether clicking on the backdrop dismisses the modal.
        • null: The backdrop is displayed, but clicking on it has no effect.
        • true: The backdrop is displayed, and clicking on it dismisses the dialog.
        • false: The backdrop is not displayed.
        Defaults to null.
        Parameters:
        backdrop -
